Creating Lasting Friendships Since 1982
Enjoy a lifestyle defined by reverence of the game's heritage, commitment to an active lifestyle, and an authentic tradition of community. Whether you are looking to purchase property within our Southwest Florida Community or simply want to rent a house for a month or two in Fort Myers to see what all the buzz is about, Fiddlesticks is the perfect community along the Gulf Coast of Florida.
End Mini-Page 20732

Begin Mini-Page 20734
We Have a Place for You!
Discover a sense of belonging within our gates, where genuine camaraderie creates a community you'll proudly call home. With just 585 homes and two golf courses, our distinctive low density sets us apart. Explore a range of living options, including condos, townhomes, and single-family residences. Begin your home search now at Fiddlesticks Country Club.
View Properties
View Membership Information

Rent at Fiddlesticks and Experience the Lifestyle.
Join our expansive rental program and enjoy membership perks for a month, two, or even three. Live, play, and savor the complete Fiddlesticks experience. Once you're here, you won't want to say goodbye.
Rental Listings by Owner
Rental Listings by Agent
View Rental Information

Begin Mini-Page 20738
Whether you are a resident equity, non-resident, or a tennis member, you are part of the Fiddlesticks family.
At Fiddlesticks, membership is required upon home purchase, with all members in the gates as equal members. Limited non-resident and tennis memberships are available for those seeking exclusive access.

Southwest Florida Living, Redefined!

Make Fiddlesticks Your Home!
Unlock the door to the Fiddlesticks way of life. From estate sized lots to premier amenities, our community beckons you. Call us today for more information and let the journey to your dream living experience begin.
Explore Further Details
